Tenant-domain views (easy)
log_audit(
    request=request,
    tenant=request.tenant,
    action=AuditAction.USER_UPDATED,
    target=user,
)

Platform admin / shared schema (explicit)
log_audit(
    request=request,
    tenant=tenant,  # you already fetched it
    action=AuditAction.INVITE_SENT,
    metadata={"email": email},
)